Miss Estella Mutale uyo ane makore makumi mana ne mashanu akauya kubva kure kose uko ku Zambia kusvika pa SCOAN

0:00:08.460,0:00:11.640
ne dambudziko re HIV / AIDS Positive 1.

0:00:11.640,0:00:16.920
Iyi ndiyo tsamba ye wezvehutano inobva ku Ministry of Health, Ndola Central Hospital mu Zambia,

0:00:16.920,0:00:21.560
kuedza nekusimbisa kuti ane HIV/AIDS Positive 1.

0:00:21.560,0:00:26.580
Auya achitenda kuti Jesu Kristu achamuporesa muzita Rake Dzvene.

0:00:26.600,0:00:28.020
Ngatinzwei kubva kwaari.

0:00:28.020,0:00:32.260
Zita rangu ndi Miss Estella Mutale, ndakabva ku Zambia.

0:00:32.260,0:00:35.500
Ndine makore makumi mana nemashanu.

0:00:35.500,0:00:41.120
Ndine HIV / AIDS Positive 1.

0:00:41.120,0:00:46.700
Tiudze zita rechipatara chakakuedza ne kusimbisa kuti une HIV / AIDS Positive 1.

0:00:46.700,0:00:49.140
Ndola Central Hospital, Zambia.

0:00:49.140,0:00:56.640
Ndinonzwa kushaya simba, handina chido chekudya uye ndinorwadziwa ne musoro.

0:00:56.640,0:01:02.520
Chii chakakonzera HIV/AIDS Positive 1 muupenyu hwenyu?

0:01:02.520,0:01:05.940
Upombwe ne chihure.

0:01:05.940,0:01:09.400
Manga uine dambudziko iri re HIV/AIDS Positive1 kwe nguva yakadii?

0:01:09.400,0:01:10.780
Makore masere.

0:01:10.780,0:01:15.740
Iye zvino zvauri pano pa SCOAN, unotenda kuti Mwari Wamasimba Ose achakuitira chii?

0:01:15.740,0:01:19.600
Ndinotenda kuti ndichaporeswa, muzita ra Jesu.

0:01:19.600,0:01:24.060
Nguva Ye Kuporeswa

0:01:24.060,0:01:43.480
Mu Porofita T.B. Joshua achishumira munyengetero ne kuporesa muzita ra Jesu

0:01:43.480,0:01:46.120
Mudzimai wangu.

0:01:46.120,0:01:47.600
Chii chawakaita kwaari?

0:01:47.600,0:01:49.520
ihosha ipi yawakamupa?

0:01:49.520,0:01:58.320
Ndakamupa HIV/AIDS ne mapundu muchibereko.

0:01:58.320,0:02:00.740
Kuratidzira Kwe Mweya Wakaipa

0:02:00.760,0:02:03.260
Ndakamupa chirwere cheganda.

0:02:03.260,0:02:04.420
Chii chawakaita kumuchato wake?

0:02:04.420,0:02:07.760
Hapana muchato. Mudzimai wangu.

0:02:07.760,0:02:09.760
Wakaitei kune basa rake?

0:02:09.760,0:02:13.100
Hapana basa, kukundikana kwe bhizinesi.

