Anunurwa Mu Zita ra Jesu

0:02:26.200,0:02:27.860
Kuna Mwari ngakuve ne kubwinya.

0:02:27.860,0:02:29.280
Asununguka.

0:02:29.280,0:02:33.680
Uchapupu Hunopfuurira

0:02:33.680,0:02:36.560
Hareruya! Wagamuchirwa, muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:02:36.560,0:02:39.540
Ndapota tiudze zita rako uye kwaunobva.

0:02:39.540,0:02:44.140
Zita rangu ndi Miss Estella Mutale, ini ndinobva ku Zambia.

0:02:44.140,0:02:47.480
Uchapupu hwangu hwakamira seizvi:

0:02:47.480,0:03:02.280
Muna 2008, ndakatanga kunzwa zvisinganzwisisiki - mhezi muviri wangu wose, zvirwere, mumuviri wangu.

0:03:02.280,0:03:03.940
Ndakashaya chido che kudya.

0:03:03.940,0:03:08.820
mhezi mumuviri wangu wose.

0:03:08.820,0:03:22.000
Muna 2008, ndakaenda kuchipatara, uye ndakaedzwa ndikaonekwa ndine HIV / AIDS Positive 1.

0:03:22.000,0:03:30.400
Ndakadzokera kumba ndokuudza mhuri yangu nezvazvo.

0:03:30.400,0:03:36.240
Mwanakomana wangu akandiudza nezve Emmanuel TV.

0:03:36.240,0:03:37.600
Hareruya!

0:03:37.600,0:03:40.120
Saka, tinogona kunzwisisa kuti hanzvadzi yedu iri kubva nekupi.

0:03:40.120,0:03:43.020
Ati akanga ane dambudziko re HIV / AIDS Positive 1.

0:03:43.020,0:03:48.480
Tinongoda kuti iwe unyanye kutitaurira zvakanyanya nezvekuti dambudziko iri rakakanganisa hupenyu hwako sei.

0:03:48.480,0:03:53.720
Musi wawaudzwa na vanachiremba kuti iwe une HIV / AIDS wakanzwa sei?

0:03:53.720,0:04:02.220
Ndakanzwa zvakaipa. Ndakanga ndichirara masikati ne usiku

0:04:02.220,0:04:11.060
nokuti chiremba akandiudza kuti hapana mushonga wechirwere ichi.

0:04:11.060,0:04:17.980
Ndaitya kuti ndaizofa chero nguva.

0:04:17.980,0:04:22.600
Ndezvipi zviratidzo zvawakave nazvo mumakore nekuda kwe HIV/AIDS?

0:04:22.600,0:04:25.740
Ufeve uye upombwe.

0:04:25.740,0:04:27.560
Iwe unoreva kuti ndicho chaiva chikonzero?

0:04:27.560,0:04:28.740
Hongu

0:04:28.740,0:04:33.180
Asi zvatanga tichibvunza ndezvekuti: HIV yakakanganisa iwe ne hutano hwako sei?

0:04:33.180,0:04:36.940
Ndeipi matambudziko awakave nawo nawo nekuda kwe HIV?

0:04:36.940,0:04:38.860
Yakanga ichindikanganisa.

0:04:38.860,0:04:42.520
Ndakanga ndiri mudzimai webhizimisi. Handaikwanisa kuita chero chinhu.

0:04:42.520,0:04:46.100
Ndaigara ndirere pamubhedha.

0:04:46.100,0:04:50.700
Zvakaita kuti ndisadiwe, uye ndaiva nemweya wekutya.

0:04:50.700,0:04:59.020
Pandaibuda ne kukwira bhazi, pfungwa dzangu dzaindiudza  kuti ndaizofa.

0:04:59.020,0:05:02.740
Ipapo, mwanakomana wangu akandiudza nezve Emmanuel TV.

0:05:02.740,0:05:07.540
Ndakatanga kuona Emmanuel TV 24/7.

0:05:07.540,0:05:18.860
Rimwe zuva rakakosha, ndakaona mukadzi aibva ku Botswana achipupurira nezvokuporeswa kubva ku HIV /AIDS.

0:05:18.860,0:05:24.180
Saka, ndakakurudzirwa uye kutenda kwangu kwakatanga kukura.

0:05:24.180,0:05:31.740
Ndakasarudza kuuya ku SCOAN muna 2015.

0:05:31.740,0:05:36.260
Munhu wa Mwari akandinamatira.

0:05:36.260,0:05:49.440
Mazuva maviri mushure mekunge mu Porofita T.B. Joshua andinamatira, zvose - zvirwere, mhezi,  - zvakanyangarika.

0:05:49.440,0:05:55.100
Hareruya! Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Jesu!

0:05:55.100,0:05:59.900
Tinogona kuona pasikirini, nguva iyo hanzvadzi yedu yakagamuchira munyengetero kubva ku mu Porofita T.B. Joshua,

0:05:59.900,0:06:01.520
muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:06:01.520,0:06:06.780
Mweya wakaipa uyo waiva shure kwehurwere hwake hwe HIV/AIDS wakatanga kuratidzira.

0:06:06.780,0:06:10.940
Panguva iyoyo yekudzikinurwa, chii chawakanzwa?

0:06:10.940,0:06:15.240
Ini ndanaka, zvose (zve HIV) zvakanyangarika.

0:06:15.240,0:06:19.800
Zvadaro, ndakadzokera kumba kunyika yangu Zambia.

0:06:19.800,0:06:27.400
Muna January 2016, ndakadzokera kuchipatara chimwechetecho

0:06:27.400,0:06:29.740
Chaiva chipatara chipi?

0:06:29.740,0:06:33.840
University Teaching Hospital in Zambia.

0:06:33.840,0:06:38.600
Ndakawanika ndisina HIV/AIDS.

0:06:38.600,0:06:43.940
Hareruya! Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Jesu!

0:06:43.940,0:06:47.580
Chokwadi, kuna Mwari, hapana chinhu chinotadzika. Ameni!

0:06:47.580,0:06:51.140
Kana iwe uchiziva kuti Mwari Wemasimba Ose achaita kuti zvisingagoneki zvako zvive zvinogoneka,

0:06:51.140,0:06:56.640
Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Jesu!

0:06:56.640,0:06:57.640
Hareruya!

0:06:57.660,0:07:03.500
Sezvo iwe wakaedzwa ukaonekwa usina (HIV) nenyasha dza Mwari, mushure memunyengetero kubva kumunhu wa Mwari,

0:07:03.500,0:07:07.660
tiudze hupenyu hwako hurisei iye zvino uye uri kunzwa sei?

0:07:07.660,0:07:14.060
Ndinofara zvikuru.

0:07:14.060,0:07:15.960
Ini ndakanaka!

0:07:15.960,0:07:20.860
Ko zvakadini nemhezi dzawaive nadzo? Zvakadini nebasa rako? Wakadzokera kubasa here?

0:07:20.860,0:07:25.980
Zvose zvakanyangarika, ndakanaka.

0:07:25.980,0:07:31.000
Isa maoko ako pamwe chete kuna Jesu zvakare!

0:07:31.000,0:07:35.560
Wakadzokera kumabasa rako here? Uye bhizinesi rako riri sei zvino, mushure mekuporeswa kwako?

0:07:35.560,0:07:44.140
Panguva yechiwere ichocho che HIV/AIDS, ndaive nemweya we zvipingidzo, kurambwa,

0:07:44.140,0:07:51.080
zvose zvandaibata ne maoko angu zvaisashanda.

0:07:51.080,0:07:54.880
Asi ikozvino, mushure mekusunungurwa, zvinhu zvashanduka sei mune bhizinesi rako?

0:07:54.880,0:07:58.920
Zvinhu zvese zvachinja.

0:07:58.920,0:08:03.340
Hareruya! Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu kamwe zvakare!

0:08:03.340,0:08:07.100
Tiri kuona magwaro pabhodhi iri pedyo newe.

0:08:07.100,0:08:12.020
Ungagone here kuti tsanangurira isu chimwe ne chimwe kuti zvii?

0:08:12.020,0:08:22.000
Rekutanga ndere zvakawanikwa pakuyedzwa kwe HIV/AIDS Positive 1: Tsigiro yekuva ne HIV/Positive 1.

0:08:22.000,0:08:36.760
Mushure memunamato kubva kumunhu wa Mwari, ndakadzokera kuchipatara uye ndakaedzwa ndikaonekwa ndisina HIV/AIDS.

0:08:36.760,0:08:42.280
Ndakawanikwa ndisina chero chinhu pazvose.

0:08:42.280,0:08:46.340
Hareruya! Isa maoko ako pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu, Muponesi Mukuru!

0:08:46.340,0:08:58.520
