0:08:58.520,0:09:01.960
Hareruya! Mwari akanaka, nguva dzose!

0:09:01.960,0:09:08.800
Tinoda kunzwa izwi rako reyambiro kune vanhu varikukuona pasi rose.

0:09:08.800,0:09:20.420
Vanhu pasi pose, kunyanya vakadzi vasina kuroorwa vakaita seni, yambiro yangu ndeye kuti munofanira kugara kure nechivi.

0:09:20.420,0:09:23.680
Rambai makatendeka kuna Mwari.

